#question(tags: ("calculation","變異數", "平均數"))[
  十三、設一組資料為 $x_1, x_2, ..., x_n$，$mu_x$ 與 $sigma^2_x$ 分別為其平均數與變異數。若有另一組資料為 $y_i=a x_i+b$ ($i=1,2,...,n$) ($a, b$ 為常數)，試問此組資料的平均數與變異數分別為何？
][
  - 平均數：
    $
    &mu_x = sum x / N \
    => &mu_y = sum (a x + b) / N \
    => &mu_y = sum (a x) / N + sum b / N \
    => &mu_y = a times 1/N sum x + b \
    => &mu_y = a times mu_x + b

    $
  - 變異數：
    $
    &sigma_x^2 = (sum (x - mu_x)^2)/N \
    => &sigma_y^2 = (sum (y - mu_y)^2)/N \
    => &sigma_y^2 = (sum (a x_i + b - a mu_x - b)^2)/N \
    => &sigma_y^2 = (sum (a x_i - a mu_x)^2)/N \
    => &sigma_y^2 = a^2/N sum (x_i - mu_x)^2 \
    => &sigma_y^2 = a^2 sigma_x^2
    $
]

